Package de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAccessor
    The interface IAccessor models the root of a hierarchy of derived interfaces.
    IContainerItemAccessor<T>
    The interface IContainerItemAccess models a generic accessor for items in a container such as an Array or a List or a Map.
    IContainerPropertyAccessor
    The interface IContainerPropertyAccessor models an accessor for all container like properties such as Arrays, Lists, and Maps.
    IPropertyAccessor
    The interface IPropertyAccessor models an accessor for accessing the annotated fields in a POJO.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
    AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Array properties.
    AbstractContainerItemAccessorImpl<T>
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and provides default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
    AbstractContainerPropertyAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerPropertyAccessor interface.
    AbstractListItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all List like properties.
    AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Map like properties.
    AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IPropertyAccessor interface.
    ArrayPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class ArrayPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, representing the root of a hierarchy of accessors.
    BranchArrayItemAccessorImpl
    The final class BranchArrayItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in ArrayS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
    BranchListItemAccessorImpl
    The final class BranchListItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in ListS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
    BranchMapItemAccessorImpl
    The final class BranchMapItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in MapS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
    BranchPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class BranchPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing properties that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
    DefaultTypeMapperImpl
    The class DefaultTypeMapperImpl models a concrete implementation of the ITypeMapper interface, with support for only the standard Java types such as java.lang.Boolean and java.math.BigDecimal including generic Enum support.
    DefaultValueHolder
    The class DefaultValueHolder models a holder for a default value which was declared by the Property annotation's defaultValue property.
    LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl
    The final class LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of ArrayS, such as Integer or EnumS.
    LeafListItemAccessorImpl
    The final class LeafListItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of ListS, such as Integer or EnumS.
    LeafMapItemAccessorImpl
    The final class LeafMapItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of MapS, such as Integer or EnumS.
    LeafPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class LeafPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type fields, such as Integer or EnumS.
    ListPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class ListPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing all List type properties.
    MapPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class MapPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing all Map type properties.
    RootAccessorBuilder
    The final class RootAccessorBuilder models a builder for instances of the IAccessor interface that represent the root of a hierarchy of accessors for traversing and accessing the properties of instances of classes that have been annotated with the PropertyClass annotation.
    RootAccessorImpl
    The final class RootAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, representing the root of a hierarchy of accessors.
